<!-- Pricing Section -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-charcoal mb-6">
        Here's What It Actually Costs
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        No games, no "call for pricing." Just honest numbers from someone who's been on both sides of the table.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pricing Cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
      
      <!-- Discovery Call Card -->
      <div class="relative bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 pb-20 border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-coral-400 transition-all hover:shadow-lg flex flex-col">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-charcoal mb-2">The Discovery Call</h3>
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">$500</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">(but hear me out)</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-gray-700 mb-8 flex-grow space-y-4">
          <p>I'll spend an hour or so digging into what's actually eating your day. You get a complete roadmap of what to automate first, what it'll cost, and how much time you'll get back.</p>
          
          <p>If you move forward, this $500 gets credited to your project. If you don't, you still have a plan you can use however you want.</p>
          
          <p class="text-sm italic">Why I charge for this: Because free consultations are sales pitches. Paid ones are honest assessments.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-center">
          100% credited if you proceed
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Real Work Card -->
      <div class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-coral-50 to-coral-100 rounded-2xl p-8 pb-20 border-2 border-coral-500 shadow-xl transform scale-105 mt-4 flex flex-col">
        <div class="absolute -top-4 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
          <span class="bg-coral-500 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Most Popular</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-charcoal mb-2">The Real Work</h3>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Starting at $1,500</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Every business is different</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-gray-700 mb-8 flex-grow space-y-4">
          <p>Every business is different. A plumber's automation needs aren't the same as a law firm's. After our discovery call, you'll know exactly what your project costs.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-white/70 rounded-lg p-4 space-y-2">
            <p class="font-semibold">Simple stuff: $1,500-2,500</p>
            <p class="text-sm">(like automated invoice reminders)</p>
            
            <p class="font-semibold mt-3">Complex systems: $3,500-8,000</p>
            <p class="text-sm">(like full client onboarding workflows)</p>
          </div>
          
          <p class="font-medium">No surprises. No scope creep. The price we agree on is the price you pay.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 bg-coral-500 text-white px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-center">
          2-3 week turnaround
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Keeping It Running Card -->
      <div class="relative bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8 pb-20 border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-coral-400 transition-all hover:shadow-lg flex flex-col">
        <div class="text-center mb-6">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-charcoal mb-2">Keeping It Running</h3>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">$400-800/month</div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">(Optional)</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-gray-700 mb-8 flex-grow space-y-4">
          <p>Automations need care as your business grows. I'll monitor everything, fix what breaks, and optimize as you scale. Most clients choose this because peace of mind is worth $400.</p>
          
          <p class="font-medium">Month-to-month. Cancel anytime. No hard feelings.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-center">
          Optional - month to month
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    
    <!-- How This Works Section -->
    <div class="bg-navy-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-6 text-center">
        How this works:
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/90 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Most of my clients save 20+ hours per week within the first month. At $50/hour (conservative), that's $1,000/week in your time back. The automation pays for itself pretty quickly.
      </p>
      
      <div class="text-center border-t border-white/20 pt-8">
        <p class="text-xl font-semibold mb-6">
          The bottom line: I'm not the cheapest option. I'm the "get it done right the first time" option.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="mailto:tom@ctbusinessautomations.com" class="bg-coral-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-coral-400 transition-all hover:scale-105 transform inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            <span>Let's Talk</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/case-studies" class="border-2 border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-navy-900 transition-all">
            See Examples First
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>